casebody.data:
John ADAMS and Gerald McConahy, Intervening Creditors, Appellants, v. CITY OF SARASOTA, FLORIDA, a Municipal Corporation, a Municipal Debtor, Appellee. No. 8060. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. Oct. 24, 1936.

Before FOSTER, SIBLEY, and HUTCHESON, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The petition for rehearing in the above numbered and entitled cause is denied.
